<Layout>
  <Hero image={heroPhoto} alt="Danse au Parc des Bastions" />

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-prose w-full py-8">
    <Image
      src={logo}
      alt="Backbeat logo"
      class="text-center mx-auto pb-6"
      height={150}
    />
    <p class="text-stone-800 pb-3">
      For a few years now, Backbeat has been sharing its enthusiasm for swing
      and jazz dances.
    </p>
    <p class="text-stone-800 pb-3">
      Joining Backbeat means joining a curious and passionate community, driven
      by the desire to explore jazz, its music, its dances and the
      African-American culture that gave birth to them.
    </p>
    <p class="text-stone-800 pb-3">
      It also means joining a group that is committed to creating spaces for
      emancipation, meeting and mutual recognition for everyone.
    </p>
  </section>

  <MoreSoon />

